THIS 2023 HERA FLOORPLAN BUILT BY CASTLEROCK BOASTS A SPACIOUS OPEN FLOORPLAN (3 BR/2 FULL BATHS), HUGE ENTERTAINING ISLAND, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, TIMELESS & DURABLE LVP FLOORING, SS APPLIANCES, UPGRADED CEILING FANS IN BEDROOMS, NEW LIGHTING FIXTURES, RING SECURITY SYSTEM, TANKLESS WATER HEATER & MUCH MORE! THIS STUNNING COMMUNITY IS LOCATED LESS THAN TWO MILES EAST OF SH288, WHICH PROVIDES EASY ACCES TO THE GULF COAST, THE AREA'S PETROCHEMICAL EMPLOYMENT COMPLEX AND TO HOUSTON.  ENJOY THE BEAUTIFUL OUTDOORS WITH LAKES, RECREATION AMENTITIES, TRAILS AND TREE PRESERVATION AREAS. MAKE AN APPOINTMENT TODAY!
